Review: The stick is quite brittle - I weight 60kg and it broke when I was climbing stairs while using the umbrella for support. The canopy vent helps with the wind, but if you keep the umbrella upside down (as you normally would) after using it, water from the bottom canopy will flow inside the umbrella and then on your hand if you use the umbrella again before it completely dries out. I also wish the handle was a hook so that I could hang it when I need both hands while not using the umbrella.
